<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; 
            line-height: 1.8; 
            color: #333; 
            max-width: 600px; 
            margin: 0 auto; 
            padding: 20px; 
            background-color: #f0f4f8; 
        }
        h1 { 
            color: #2980b9; 
            font-size: 24px; 
        }
        p { 
            font-size: 16px; 
        }
        .order-details { 
            background-color: #ffffff; 
            border: 1px solid #dcdcdc; 
            border-radius: 8px; 
            padding: 20px; 
            margin-top: 20px; 
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); 
        }
        .order-details p { 
            margin: 10px 0; 
        }
        .order-details strong { 
            color: #2c3e50; 
        }
        .order-items { 
            margin-top: 20px; 
            background-color: #f9fafb; 
            border-radius: 5px; 
            padding: 15px; 
            border: 1px solid #e1e4e8; 
        }
        .item { 
            padding: 10px 0; 
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef; 
        }
        .item:last-child { 
            border-bottom: none; 
        }
        .footer { 
            margin-top: 30px; 
            font-size: 14px; 
            color: #7f8c8d; 
            text-align: center; 
        }
        .btn { 
            display: inline-block; 
            background-color: #3498db; 
            color: #fff; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            padding: 10px 20px; 
            border-radius: 5px; 
            margin-top: 15px; 
            font-weight: bold; 
        }
        .btn:hover { 
            background-color: #2980b9; 
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Order Confirmation</h1>
    <p>Thank you for your purchase! Your order has been successfully confirmed.</p>

    <div class="order-details">
        <p><strong>Order ID:</strong> <%= order._id %></p>
        <p><strong>Order Date:</strong> <%= order.date %></p>
        <p><strong>Course Name:</strong> <%= order.name %></p>
        <p><strong>Order Total:</strong> $<%= typeof order.price === 'number' ? order.price.toFixed(2) : order.price %></p>
    </div>

    <p>If you have any questions about your order, feel free to <a href="mailto:support@example.com">contact our customer support</a>.</p>
    
    <a href="#" class="btn">View Your Order</a>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Thank you for choosing our course!</p>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Online Course, Inc. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>